              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SIBAR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " 4cm**2 gold surface-barrier silicon heavy-ion",
                "detector. The  alpha-particle  calibrations  were",
                "based  on linear least-squares fits to seven",
                "alpha-particle energy standards ranging from 3.18 to",
                "8.79 MeV and  extrapolating these calibrations to the",
                "fission-fragment energy region using a high-precision",
                "pulse generator."
              ]
            }
          ],
